<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFWesson2000">Wesson, John (2000). <i><a href="http://www.jet.efda.org/documents/wesson/wesson.html" class="external text" title="http://www.jet.efda.org/documents/wesson/wesson.html" rel="nofollow">The Science of JET</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.jet.efda.org/documents/wesson/wesson.html" class="external free" title="http://www.jet.efda.org/documents/wesson/wesson.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.jet.efda.org/documents/wesson/wesson.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Science+of+JET&amp;rft.aulast=Wesson&amp;rft.aufirst=John&amp;rft.au=Wesson%2C+John&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jet.efda.org%2Fdocuments%2Fwesson%2Fwesson.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tokamak"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFWessonet_al2004">Wesson, John; et al (2004). <i>Tokamaks</i>. Oxford University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198509227" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-850922-7</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Tokamaks&amp;rft.aulast=Wesson&amp;rft.aufirst=John&amp;rft.au=Wesson%2C+John&amp;rft.au=et+al&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-19-850922-7&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tokamak"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
